snippet.title: Cursetorn - Will You Survive Till The Next Day? Not When I'm in Charge...
snippet.description:
Cursetorn is a GameJam horror game about you and a patient trying to survive night by night. Patient may or may not have nice long hair.

Game Info: https://pumamori.itch.io/cursetorn

"Return the slabbbbbb."
